s of architectonics and the singular quality of housing features. These continue to mark theoretical thinking even as they dissolve and withdraw, as in Heidegger's "house of Being."  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362708640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503627086423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503627086/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles